high_descs: Go to the end of the island across from the door.
Pick up a knife on the island.
Move left to the other end of the island.
Slice the loaf of bread on the island.
Turn around and go to the fridge.
Put the knife in the fridge.
Go back to the island with the sliced bread.
Pick up a slice of bread on the island.
Go to the fridge.
Cool off the bread in the fridge.
Go to the microwave.
Put the cold bread in the microwave.
anns.task_desc: Put a cold piece of bread in the microwave.

high_descs: Go across the room and turn left to look at the counter.
Pick up the knife on the counter.
Turn left and move further down the counter to the bread.
Cut the bread on the counter.
Turn left and go to the fridge.
Put the knife in the freezer in front of the lettuce.
Turn around and go back to the bread on the counter.
Pick up a slice of bread.
Go around the counter and head back to the fridge.
Put the slice of bread in the fridge to chill and take it back out.
Turn right, go across the room and turn left to face the microwave.
Put the slice of bread in the microwave.
anns.task_desc: Put a chilled slice of bread in the microwave.

high_descs: Take a right to the stove, turn left and walk to the right side of the counter on the left.
Pick up the knife with the yellow handle on the right side of the counter.
Turn left and walk to the left side of the counter on the right.
Slice the loaf of bread on the counter.
Turn left, hang a right at the counter and walk to the fridge.
Put the knife on the top shelf in the middle inside the fridge and close the door.
Turn around, hang a left at the stove and walk to the counter on the left.
Pick up a slice of bread from the loaf on the counter.
Turn left and walk to the fridge on the right.
Put the slice of bread inside the fridge on the top wire shelf in the middle, chill it, remove it and close the door.
Turn around, hang a left at the wall and walk to the microwave on the counter.
Put the chilled slice of bread in the microwave.
anns.task_desc: Chill a knife inside a fridge and place a slice of chilled bread inside a microwave.
